Tutorial
=============

Itroduction
-----------
We offer TrainT,Train,Test,Debug functions.
TrainT is a integerated way to train.

Inside process
-----------
data process flow buildin includes:
    get_raw:    get (X,y) from file
    pre:        change X to better form.
    (grid_search: for train)
    ext:        extract feature from X.
    sel:        slect feature.
    clf:        classification. 
Refer to help for detailed and complete information.

Learning process
-----------
Follow these steps to get familar with our API.
1. see templates
2. see help(TrainT Train Test Debug)
2. see example/

Workflow Using TrainT
----------
1. prepare balanced data
2. choose a .py from templates or make yourself; config.
3. run and check.got back to [2] to update , userdictionary, stopwords, select.k, clf.params, etc.
[4.] use final .py and other config to train all data to get final model.set pfrac=0, cv=1.

Deploy
---------
After train, model should be deployed to text_platform_service.
use deploy
